title: FClones just got automatic file deduplication feature
selftext:
My fast duplicate file finder written in Rust has just become also a fast duplicate file remover! 

This is probably the biggest release since many months.

[https://github.com/pkolaczk/fclones/releases/tag/v0.12.0](https://github.com/pkolaczk/fclones/releases/tag/v0.12.0)
